  "text": [
    "at neck, at",
    "shoulder, that",
    "stokes a man",
    "as he grows",
    "older. Nothing",
    "rages, nothing",
    "fumes. No one",
    "races through",
    "the rooms,",
    "alarmed. How",
    "casually he's",
    "armed. How",
    "gradually arises",
    "what surprises",
    "in his mirrors.",
    "Unawares, as",
    "fall runs colder,",
    "pulls he only",
    "slightly tighter",
    "his good wool",
    "sweater, thinner",
    "than ever now",
    "at elbow,",
    "at shoulder."
  ],
  "title": "How Smokes the Smolder",
  "year": ""
}